'''Hassan Bernoussi''' ({{lang-ar|حسن برنوصي}}; born 1965–[[rabat]]) is a Moroccan businessman and CEO of the group ''Interface''. He was the director of Morocco's department of foreign investments for 14 years.<ref>{{cite news|title=Investissements Bernoussi dépose sa démission|url=http://www.maghress.com/fr/lagazette/18051|accessdate=15 December 2013|newspaper=La Gazette du Maroc|date=25 July 2008}}</ref> He studied at the school of [[Mohammed VI of Morocco|Mohammed VI]]'s late cousin Nawfal along with [[Mounir Majidi]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Son entourage: douze jeunes hommes programmés. Ils ont fréquenté les mêmes bancs du Collège royal.|url=http://www.liberation.fr/evenement/1999/08/24/son-entourage-douze-jeunes-hommes-programmes-ils-ont-frequente-les-memes-bancs-du-college-royal_280773|accessdate=15 December 2013|newspaper=Libération|date=24 August 1999|author=José Garçon}}</ref>
